---
const cdnBase = 'https://portfolio-image-cdn.zongxz66.workers.dev';
const { project } = Astro.props as { project: any };
const heroTitle = project.data.title?.split(' — ')[0] ?? project.data.title;
const heroSubtitle = project.data.subtitle ?? project.data.title?.split(' — ')[1] ?? '';
const heroSummary = project.data.summary;
---

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" crossorigin />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" />

<main class="p1-root">
  <section class="p1-hero">
    <div class="p1-hero-shell">
      <div class="p1-hero-media" aria-hidden="true">
        <img
          src={`${cdnBase}/project-1/cover.jpg`}
          alt=""
          class="p1-hero-img"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="p1-hero-copy">
        <p class="p1-caption p1-hero-caption">{heroTitle} / project 01</p>

        <div class="p1-kicker-row">
          <span class="p1-hero-index">01</span>
          <span class="p1-kicker-line"></span>
          <span class="p1-kicker-text">工业设计 / 智能穿戴 / 医疗机能</span>
        </div>

        <div class="p1-copy-stack">
          <p class="p1-overline">case study</p>
          <h1 class="p1-hero-title">{heroTitle}</h1>
          <p class="p1-hero-sub">{heroSubtitle}</p>
        </div>

        <p class="p1-hero-desc">{heroSummary}</p>

        <div class="p1-hero-tags">
          <span>AFO 三点力学矫形</span>
          <span>柔性压力传感监测</span>
          <span>模块化磁吸快穿脱</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-context">
    <div class="p1-rect-grid p1-rect-grid--context">
      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-context-merged">
        <div class="p1-context-copy-panel">
          <p class="p1-context-title">痉挛性脑性瘫痪发病率高，步态问题突出。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p1-context-detail-panel">
          <p class="p1-context-body">
            痉挛性脑瘫是儿童高发的运动障碍疾病，足部肌张力紊乱常引发足内翻，造成重心偏移、步态不稳与更高跌倒风险。与此同时，患儿往往难以准确表达疼痛与不适，传统矫形器又普遍外观医疗化，容易带来病耻感与穿戴抗拒。市场仍缺少兼顾步态数据采集、医患沟通与儿童审美的智能矫形设备。
          </p>

          <div class="p1-stat-rail">
            <div class="p1-stat">
              <span class="p1-stat-note">每千名活产婴儿脑瘫发病率</span>
              <div class="p1-stat-row">
                <span class="p1-stat-num">2–3.4</span>
                <span class="p1-stat-unit">例</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p1-stat">
              <span class="p1-stat-note">其中痉挛型占比</span>
              <div class="p1-stat-row">
                <span class="p1-stat-num">75</span>
                <span class="p1-stat-unit">%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <figure class="p1-context-media">
          <img
            src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMHajEen4wRm27yrMh7iw4AAfFaq-A2AALqEWsbbjqJVbS5QfLRy_q0AQADAgADdwADPAQ.png"
            alt="背景调研图"
          />
        </figure>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-pain">
    <div class="p1-pain-grid">
      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-pain-card">
        <figure class="p1-pain-media p1-pain-media--a">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMMajFexxuqLKbtPJMakJpLUs53BJUAAhETaxtuOolVWYdoNIcc9CoBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="足内翻痛点图" />
          <span class="p1-pain-tag">痛点 01</span>
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-pain-copy">
          <h3 class="p1-pain-title">足内翻</h3>
          <p class="p1-pain-text">足部肌张力紊乱会持续拉扯步态，导致重心偏移、步态不稳与更高跌倒风险。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-pain-card">
        <figure class="p1-pain-media p1-pain-media--b">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMNajFe_Ht_ja9cu3xVBbaGGdAB86AAAhYTaxtuOolV0Q8bZvj3L5sBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="沟通障碍痛点图" />
          <span class="p1-pain-tag">痛点 02</span>
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-pain-copy">
          <h3 class="p1-pain-title">沟通障碍</h3>
          <p class="p1-pain-text">患儿难以准确表达疼痛与不适，家长和康复师也难以及时判断真实身体状态。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-pain-card">
        <figure class="p1-pain-media p1-pain-media--c">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMOajFfI_iSaNhP-_ueoQ5pVEwsj2EAAhcTaxtuOolVsQXYrrG-hiIBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="病耻感痛点图" />
          <span class="p1-pain-tag">痛点 03</span>
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-pain-copy">
          <h3 class="p1-pain-title">病耻感</h3>
          <p class="p1-pain-text">传统矫形器医疗器械感过强，容易让孩子在校园与社交场景中产生遮挡与抗拒心理。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-positioning">
    <div class="p1-rect-grid">
      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-feature">
        <figure class="p1-feature-media p1-feature-media--cutout">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMPajFh65JmtmzYTTsGvL-_y5HB1fEAAigTaxtuOolVFdCxS_8LY0sBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="矫正功能展示图" />
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-feature-copy">
          <h2 class="p1-feature-title">矫正</h2>
          <p class="p1-feature-text">AFO 三点力学矫形，通过 F₁ 踝底、F₂ 跟骨后、F₃ 小腿前的受力关系，帮助改善足内翻步态。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-feature">
        <figure class="p1-feature-media">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMQajFiBf9u_GfuCQPri6p3tn47SMcAAikTaxtuOolVB_ArZUBgG0wBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="监测功能展示图" />
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-feature-copy">
          <h2 class="p1-feature-title">监测</h2>
          <p class="p1-feature-text">柔性传感面料 ThermoFit 嵌入鞋体结构，实时采集足底压力与步态变化，辅助康复判断。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-feature">
        <figure class="p1-feature-media">
          <img src="https://telegraph-image-90w.pages.dev/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAATqb6rsAAMRajFiKZIQ89cchJ_x-fBn07sETTAAAioTaxtuOolVN8BiMd6ySwYBAAMCAAN3AAM8BA.png" alt="模块化连接机制展示图" />
        </figure>
        <div class="p1-feature-copy">
          <h2 class="p1-feature-title">模块化连接机制</h2>
          <p class="p1-feature-text">通过清晰的模块连接与快拆逻辑，降低穿脱门槛，让结构固定、调节与日常使用更直观高效。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-dev">
    <div class="p1-rect-grid">
      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-mapping">
        <div class="p1-mapping-row">
          <span class="p1-mapping-issue">足内翻问题</span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-link" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-solution">AFO矫形</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p1-mapping-row">
          <span class="p1-mapping-issue">沟通障碍</span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-link" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-solution">智能监测模块</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p1-mapping-row">
          <span class="p1-mapping-issue">病耻感</span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-link" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="p1-mapping-solution">模块化设计</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <figure class="p1-rect-card p1-card-sketch">
        <img src={`${cdnBase}/project-1/sketch-1.jpg`} alt="设计草图" />
        <figcaption class="p1-caption">设计草图</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-copy">
        <p class="p1-overline">prototype</p>
        <h2 class="p1-body-title">将微型智能硬核压进极薄鞋底夹层</h2>
        <p class="p1-body-text p1-body-text--large">
          以压电传感器 + Arduino 开发板 + 面包板搭建传感回路，分两阶段验证：平面手压测试验证传感器响应曲线的稳定性与灵敏度；粘土脚型模拟测试将传感器嵌入手塑粘土足底模型，模拟真实行走时的足底压力分布，实时采集步态波形并输出可视化曲线。
        </p>
        <p class="p1-body-text">
          从传感布局 → 信号采集 → 波形可视化，完整跑通智能监测的技术链路。
        </p>
      </article>

      <figure class="p1-rect-card p1-card-circuit">
        <img src={`${cdnBase}/project-1/circuit-schematic.jpg`} alt="Arduino 与 FSR 传感器电路原理" />
        <figcaption class="p1-caption">Arduino 与 FSR 传感器电路原理</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <aside class="p1-rect-card p1-card-steps">
        <p class="p1-overline">workflow</p>
        <div class="p1-tech-steps">
          <div class="p1-tech-step">
            <span class="p1-tech-num">①</span>
            <div>
              <strong>传感布局</strong>
              <p>压电传感器 + 面包板搭建传感回路，确定足底关键监测点位。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-tech-step">
            <span class="p1-tech-num">②</span>
            <div>
              <strong>信号采集</strong>
              <p>Arduino 回路验证，FSR 薄膜压力传感器实时读取模拟信号。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-tech-step">
            <span class="p1-tech-num">③</span>
            <div>
              <strong>波形可视化</strong>
              <p>步态压力数据实时输出为可视化波形曲线。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-code">
        <div class="p1-code-block">
          <div class="p1-code-header">
            <span class="p1-code-dot"></span>
            <span class="p1-code-dot"></span>
            <span class="p1-code-dot"></span>
            <span class="p1-code-label">Arduino — FSR 压力差值异常与步态判定</span>
          </div>
          <pre><code>const int FSR_INNER = A0;  // 内侧传感器
const int FSR_OUTER = A1;  // 外侧传感器

void setup() &#123;
  Serial.begin(9600);
&#125;

void loop() &#123;
  int innerVal = analogRead(FSR_INNER);
  int outerVal = analogRead(FSR_OUTER);
  if ((innerVal - outerVal) &gt; 350) &#123;
    triggerAlert();
  &#125;
  delay(50);
&#125;</code></pre>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-final">
    <div class="p1-rect-grid">
      <figure class="p1-rect-card p1-card-final-image">
        <img src={`${cdnBase}/project-1/cover.jpg`} alt="Gradient 最终呈现效果图" />
        <figcaption class="p1-caption">高帮运动鞋廓形，消解传统矫形器的医疗器械感。</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-final-copy">
        <p class="p1-overline">final result</p>
        <h2 class="p1-body-title">外刚内柔的双层异质拼接</h2>
        <p class="p1-body-text p1-body-text--large">
          主色浅蓝灰 + 蓝粉渐变装饰件（呼应 Gradient）。厚底流线型大底，兼顾缓震功能与运动视觉感。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-cmf">
        <p class="p1-overline">cmf breakdown</p>
        <div class="p1-cmf-list">
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:#a8c8e8"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>硬质外壳</strong>
              <span>医用硬质硅胶 — AFO 三点力矫正支撑</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:#d4a0d4"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>内衬面料</strong>
              <span>ThermoFit 柔性传感织物 — 实时步态监测</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:#b8d8c8"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>鞋舌 / 内里</strong>
              <span>拼接透气网面 — 长时穿戴舒适性</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:#e0d8c8"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>绑带</strong>
              <span>3 条可调节绑带 — 围度自适应固定</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6ea8d8,#d4a0d4)"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>卡扣</strong>
              <span>蓝粉渐变磁吸机械锁扣 ×2 — 快拆快装 + 视觉亮点</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-cmf-item">
            <span class="p1-cmf-swatch" style="background:#888"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>大底</strong>
              <span>厚底缓震结构 — 步态稳定 + 流线造型</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-flow">
        <p class="p1-overline">interaction flow</p>
        <h3 class="p1-card-title">五步使用流程</h3>
        <div class="p1-flow-steps">
          <div class="p1-flow-step">
            <span class="p1-flow-char">穿</span>
            <span class="p1-flow-label">脚跟贴合最深处</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="p1-flow-step">
            <span class="p1-flow-char">套</span>
            <span class="p1-flow-label">磁吸连接稳定</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="p1-flow-step">
            <span class="p1-flow-char">贴</span>
            <span class="p1-flow-label">绑带 + 卡扣紧固</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="p1-flow-step p1-flow-step--active">
            <span class="p1-flow-char">联</span>
            <span class="p1-flow-label">LED 闪烁确认启动</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p1-flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="p1-flow-step">
            <span class="p1-flow-char">走</span>
            <span class="p1-flow-label">开启矫正训练</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="p1-flow-note">Step 4 的 LED 灯光反馈，让患儿感知“设备在帮助我”——将沟通障碍痛点转化为可见的情感交互节点。</p>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-note">
        <p class="p1-overline">optional detail</p>
        <div class="p1-note-strip">
          <span class="p1-note-label">自选印花</span>
          <p>鞋身表面设计可选卡通浮雕印花，儿童主动参与外观个性化——将医疗产品转化为“我的东西”，病耻感的解决方案落地于产品细节。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p1-section p1-outro">
    <div class="p1-rect-grid">
      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-summary">
        <p>
          从<span class="p1-em">脑瘫儿童面临足内翻与病耻感双重困境</span>出发，
          Gradient 通过<span class="p1-em">AFO 三点力学矫形 × 智能传感监测 × 去医疗化美学</span>回应，
          最终将冰冷的医疗器械<span class="p1-em">重构为孩子眼中“很酷的运动鞋”</span>。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-credit">
        <p class="p1-overline">credit</p>
        <p class="p1-body-text">传感原型自主搭建 · 实体草模制作 · 产品形态设计 · Arduino 代码编写</p>
      </article>

      <article class="p1-rect-card p1-card-next">
        <p class="p1-overline">next project</p>
        <a href="/projects/project-2" class="p1-next-link">
          NeuroLimb — 腿部截肢患者术后康复 VR 悬吊系统
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 10h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
  :root {
    --p1-bg: #EDF9FF;
    --p1-surface: #F7FCFF;
    --p1-surface-2: #E6F3FA;
    --p1-border: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
    --p1-text: #1a1a1a;
    --p1-text-dim: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.62);
    --p1-accent: #4a8cb8;
    --p1-accent-warm: #b87ab8;
    --p1-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #6ea8d8 28%, #d4a0d4 72%);
    --p1-code-bg: #101722;
    --p1-code-header-bg: #162130;
    --p1-measure: min(42rem, 100%);
    --p1-container: 92rem;
    --p1-section-px: clamp(0.3125rem, 1vw, 0.75rem);
    --p1-section-py: clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vh, 1rem);
  }

  .p1-root {
    background: var(--p1-bg);
    color: var(--p1-text);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vh, 5rem);
  }

  .p1-root :global(img) {
    max-width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .p1-section,
  .p1-hero {
    padding-inline: var(--p1-section-px);
  }

  .p1-section {
    padding-block: var(--p1-section-py);
  }

  .p1-hero {
    padding-block: clamp(1rem, 2.5vh, 1.5rem) clamp(0.75rem, 2vh, 1.25rem);
    background: var(--p1-bg);
  }

  .p1-hero-shell,
  .p1-rect-grid {
    width: min(var(--p1-container), 100%);
    margin-inline: 0;
  }

  .p1-hero-shell {
    position: relative;
    min-height: clamp(34rem, 78vh, 48rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    border: 1px solid var(--p1-border);
    border-radius: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: none;
    isolation: isolate;
    background: var(--p1-surface);
  }

  .p1-hero-media {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    margin: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .p1-hero-media::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--p1-bg) 0%, var(--p1-bg) 28%, transparent 68%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .p1-hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    background: var(--p1-surface-2);
  }

  .p1-hero-copy {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    width: min(100%, 38rem);
